Class CompositionalDescriptionQueryTerm

java.lang.Object
  org.obd.query.QueryTerm
      org.obd.query.CompositionalDescriptionQueryTerm

public class CompositionalDescriptionQueryTerm
extends QueryTerm

A QueryTerm for finding nodes that satisfy a CompositionalDescription

A compositional description (class expression) is in fact very similar to a query; the description provides conditions for membership.

Here we translate the description to a query for class nodes subsumed by that description. For example, if the description is: Car THAT hasColor blue AND hasMake Skoda Then the query will be And(Link(IS_A,Car), Link(hasColor,blue), Link(hasMake, skoda))
